    "instructions": [
        "Heat 1 tbsp olive oil in a skillet over medium heat. Add broccoli and saut√© for 5-6 minutes until slightly charred. Remove and set aside.",
        "Add remaining 1/2 tbsp olive oil to the skillet. Cook ground turkey, breaking it apart, until fully browned. Move turkey to one side of the pan.",
        "Add orzo to the empty side of the skillet. Toast for 1-2 minutes until fragrant and golden.",
        "Stir in lemon pepper, Dijon mustard, and lemon juice. Add 1 cup broth to deglaze the pan, then add the remaining 1.5 cups broth. Stir to combine.",
